title: Artichoke Red Vegan Market
description: A neighorbood market that's 100% vegan, opened since Dec 2009 (originally on N Orange Ave). Features a lounge area for sitting and enjoying your coffee. Stocks a range of food and goods including vegan snack foods, nutritional vitamins, supplements, soap, personal care, cleaning supplies, pet food, and other cruelty-free products. Selection of vegan wine and beer.
